# Strategy notebook — `days.md` date semantics (anti-split)

**SSOT:** [STRATEGY-NOTEBOOK-ARCHITECTURE.md — `days.md` date keys](../../docs/skill-work/work-strategy/strategy-notebook/STRATEGY-NOTEBOOK-ARCHITECTURE.md#days-md-date-semantics).

**Invariants (WORK / `strategy` / `weave`):**

- **`## YYYY-MM-DD` in `days.md`** = **weave continuity day**, not proof the operator uploaded files that calendar day.
- **Do not** add a **new** `## YYYY-MM-DD` **only** because **`Accumulator for:`**, inbox **`### … YYYY-MM-DD`**, assistant session clock, or **wire bylines** differ — consolidate; put external dates in **Links** / **Signal**; optional **weave date note** when scopes differ.
- **Operator last-ingest boundary** → fold assistant work into that **notebook day** (or episodic heading), not extra split headings.
- **`STATUS.md`** links must match **real** `days.md` anchors after consolidation.

**Weave menu** (knot-shape options before editing `days.md` on **`weave`**) is unchanged — [architecture § Entry model / Weave command](../../docs/skill-work/work-strategy/strategy-notebook/STRATEGY-NOTEBOOK-ARCHITECTURE.md#entry-model-operator-contract).
